sequenceDiagram
    autonumber

    participant Client as Client<br/>(Dashboard/CLI)
    participant Istio as Istio Gateway<br/>mTLS
    participant MR as Model Registry API<br/>8080/TCP HTTP
    participant DB as MySQL/PostgreSQL<br/>3306/5432/TCP
    participant K8sAPI as Kubernetes API<br/>6443/TCP HTTPS
    participant Ctrl as Controller Manager<br/>8081/TCP
    participant CSI as CSI Initializer<br/>(init container)
    participant S3 as S3/MinIO<br/>443/TCP HTTPS
    participant AsyncJob as Async Upload Job<br/>(Python)
    participant OCI as OCI Registry<br/>443/TCP HTTPS
    participant HF as HuggingFace Hub<br/>443/TCP HTTPS

    Note over Client,DB: Flow 1: Model Registration via REST API
    Client->>Istio: POST /api/model_registry/v1alpha3/registered_models<br/>Istio mTLS
    Istio->>MR: Forward (mTLS STRICT)
    MR->>DB: INSERT model metadata<br/>MySQL/PG protocol, Optional TLS<br/>Auth: Username/password
    DB-->>MR: OK
    MR-->>Istio: 201 Created (JSON)
    Istio-->>Client: Response

    Note over K8sAPI,Ctrl: Flow 2: InferenceService Reconciliation
    K8sAPI->>Ctrl: Watch event: InferenceService created/updated<br/>HTTPS TLS, ServiceAccount token
    Ctrl->>MR: POST /api/.../serving_environments<br/>HTTP/HTTPS, Bearer token
    MR->>DB: INSERT serving environment
    DB-->>MR: OK
    MR-->>Ctrl: 201 Created
    Ctrl->>MR: POST /api/.../inference_services<br/>Bearer token
    MR-->>Ctrl: 201 Created
    Ctrl->>K8sAPI: PATCH InferenceService (add labels/finalizer)<br/>HTTPS, ServiceAccount token

    Note over CSI,S3: Flow 3: Model Artifact Download (CSI)
    CSI->>MR: GET model artifact URI<br/>model-registry://model/version<br/>HTTP/HTTPS, Optional TLS
    MR->>DB: SELECT artifact storage URI
    DB-->>MR: s3://bucket/model-path
    MR-->>CSI: Artifact metadata with storage URI
    CSI->>S3: Download model artifacts<br/>HTTPS TLS 1.2+<br/>Provider-specific auth (AWS IAM)
    S3-->>CSI: Model files

    Note over AsyncJob,OCI: Flow 4: Async Model Upload
    AsyncJob->>S3: Download model from source<br/>HTTPS TLS 1.2+, IAM credentials
    S3-->>AsyncJob: Model files
    AsyncJob->>OCI: Push model to OCI registry<br/>HTTPS TLS 1.2+, Docker config auth<br/>(via skopeo)
    OCI-->>AsyncJob: Push complete
    AsyncJob->>MR: POST /api/.../model_artifacts<br/>HTTP/HTTPS, Bearer token
    MR->>DB: INSERT artifact record
    DB-->>MR: OK
    MR-->>AsyncJob: 201 Created
